{"id": 901, "genre": 1001, "title": "你运动坚持不下来都有哪些理由or借口？", "description": "一旦听到手机的APP提醒要做运动了，我就化身为树懒。（题图来自：Vincent Mahé）", "record_count": 3171, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702183658vc6At2DwZbPTxnMY.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-04-12T11:41:37Z", "options": [{"id": 66816, "content": "今天好累，要不休息一天", "image": null, "praise_count": 524, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 139557}, {"id": 67072, "content": "坦克碾压一切（包括自己的意志），所以我去玩wot吧。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 565151}, {"id": 66817, "content": "天冷穿太多不方便，过了这个冬天在说", "image": null, "praise_count": 116, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 565486}, {"id": 67073, "content": "脚崴了", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 566469}, {"id": 66818, "content": "跑完步小腿要长肌肉。", "image": null, "praise_count": 39, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 502849}, {"id": 67074, "content": "昨天练了", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 464199}, {"id": 181250, "content": "没人作伴", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 971162}, {"id": 66819, "content": "操场上连个帅哥都没有。失望?", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161619BiRqFYJn2Kxk7GHa.jpg", "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 565497}, {"id": 67075, "content": "身材那么好为什么还要运动?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 529216}, {"id": 66820, "content": "我被床封印了", "image": null, "praise_count": 123, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 484145}, {"id": 67076, "content": "就今天一天，休息休息吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 566483}, {"id": 67332, "content": "来大姨妈", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 554339}, {"id": 68612, "content": "下雨了，", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 216039}, {"id": 66821, "content": "今天工作已经够累了，竟然还要去健身，放过我吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 190, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 565500}, {"id": 67077, "content": "反正也坚持不了，不如就算了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 164080}, {"id": 66822, "content": "习惯不动", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136181}, {"id": 67078, "content": "外面天天下雨", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 566493}, {"id": 67334, "content": "每天走路就是运动了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 567712}, {"id": 66823, "content": "今天不锻炼没事，下次再锻炼吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 564944}, {"id": 67079, "content": "算了吧！", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161551WTyNJ2bBidgIeMoK", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 546398}, {"id": 67847, "content": "到处都是小情侣，我一个单身狗还是回去蹲着吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 569852}, {"id": 66824, "content": "只停留在嘴上说说而已，从来没有开始过。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 239389}, {"id": 67080, "content": "出汗得洗衣服，每天洗衣服太麻烦了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 182814}, {"id": 68616, "content": "今天下雨了，不用跑步了，哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 572904}, {"id": 66825, "content": "同济大学操场上晚上有500个人在跑步我没地方跑", "image": null, "praise_count": 39, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1288}, {"id": 67081, "content": "今天天气好像不适合运动呢，改天吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 561405}, {"id": 66826, "content": "反正也没啥效果", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 403751}, {"id": 67082, "content": "没有时间", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 405120}, {"id": 67083, "content": "昨天训的太累了，休息一天", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 465898}, {"id": 66828, "content": "家里的瑜伽垫太薄了我买个厚的吧厚的这个颜色不如薄的那个好看要不要两条缝在一起用啊总之想想就很累不想运动了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1288}, {"id": 67084, "content": "已经吃那么多了，明天再说", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 252201}, {"id": 66829, "content": "大姨妈打乱了我的人生", "image": null, "praise_count": 437, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1288}, {"id": 67085, "content": "我忙", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 561158}, {"id": 66830, "content": "新买的跑步鞋有点太紧了，要不要再买一双啊没预算了，先不跑了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1288}, {"id": 67086, "content": "吃太多动不了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 566547}, {"id": 67087, "content": "总有借口不运动。其实一开始下决心的时候是真的有干劲，但当你干了那么一两天，那种累的感觉给你留下了深刻的感受，所以再接着到点需要运动的时候就会产生联想，哎呀太累了好想打退堂鼓。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 566549}, {"id": 67088, "content": "大姨妈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 527752}, {"id": 66833, "content": "好喜欢大家的理由，默默存下来下次用哈哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 89616}, {"id": 67089, "content": "心里有事儿就觉得运动也是心烦意乱就不做了，知道是借口但还是会不运动", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 394294}, {"id": 66834, "content": "买好装备就去。", "image": null, "praise_count": 116, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 561859}, {"id": 67090, "content": "装备不够好", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 565610}, {"id": 67091, "content": "吃饱了不能立即运动，要不扶我起来试试？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 566570}, {"id": 66836, "content": "太懶了 第一天下載keep運動，第二天卸載了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 172925}, {"id": 67092, "content": "我做什么都需要人陪", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 367610}, {"id": 66837, "content": "懒得动", "image": null, "praise_count": 97, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 120702}, {"id": 67093, "content": "工作太忙", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 561231}, {"id": 67349, "content": "肌肉要放松", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 523560}, {"id": 66838, "content": "没吃饱没力气跑步", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 565523}, {"id": 67094, "content": "没有理由", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 565532}, {"id": 69398, "content": "腿已经很细了，再锻炼腿就没了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 577232}]}